From 3316fc06a79a5e74c80a5cd87ccb7fdc999847da Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: unknown <schwabauerbraintomas@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 18:34:00 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: HTTP API server + Python bindings + release
 benchmarks

- api_server.rs: axum-based HTTP server (store/search/status/health)
- m2m_client.py: Python client with auto-start, store/search/status
- CLI: 'serve' subcommand for HTTP mode
- Benchmarks (release, RTX 3090, 640D):
  - 10K vectors, 100 queries: GPU 25K QPS vs CPU 275 QPS (90x speedup)
  - 100K vectors, 1K queries: GPU 1.2K QPS vs CPU 841 QPS (1.4x)
  - GPU/CPU results verified matching
- Added deps: tokio, axum, tower-http, anyhow
